  "title": "🎓Event Sales Coordinator (Entry & Fresh Grads Welcomed!)",
  "description": "<p><strong>🎓 Just Graduated/ORD-ED/Looking for a Change?</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Look no further!</strong> 🚀</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>As the <strong>leading industry expert</strong>, <strong>Euphoria Organisation</strong> is the go-to outsourced sales and marketing firm that <strong>renowned businesses</strong>trust to <strong>boost their market share</strong> and <strong>increase brand awareness</strong>.<br>\nNow, we’re expanding and on the hunt for <strong>future leaders</strong> to take their careers to the next level! 🌟</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🎯 Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>💼 <strong>Conduct face-to-face sales and marketing</strong>strategies to engage potential clients</li>\n  <li>📈 <strong>Support and enhance</strong> team growth and business development</li>\n  <li>🌍 Be part of exciting projects and contribute to <strong>client success</strong>!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>🎁 What You Can Look Forward To:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>💰 <strong>Competitive salary &amp; performance bonuses</strong> – Your hard work pays off!</li>\n  <li>🎓 <strong>1-on-1 mentorship</strong> to help you grow &amp; develop</li>\n  <li>🚀 <strong>Career advancement and progression</strong>opportunities</li>\n  <li>💡 Focus on <strong>personal development</strong> to unlock your full potential</li>\n  <li>✈️ <strong>Overseas exposure</strong> and exciting travel opportunities</li>\n  <li>🎉 A <strong>dynamic, positive team culture</strong> where growth happens every day!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>✅ Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>💪 <strong>Adaptable &amp; determined</strong> to succeed in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>💼 <strong>No experience required</strong> –  We provide <strong>full training</strong> to help you excel!</li>\n  <li>🚀 <strong>Ready to learn and grow</strong> in the industry!</li>\n  <li><br></li>\n</ul>\n<p>💥 <strong>Are you the next big thing out there?</strong><br>\n 📩 <strong>Apply now</strong> and start your journey with <strong>Euphoria Organisation today</strong>! 🌟</p>",
